subSubSection.paragraph:
Female terminalia (
Figs 17–22
): unspecialized ovipositor; S8 invaginated medio-distally with short macrosetae; furca (S9) U-shaped, sclerotized throughout; bursa copulatrix cylindrical, expanded and angled 180° medially; three spermathecae present with median spermatheca larger than lateral ones, spermathecal ducts tubular with a distinct smoothly angled banana-shaped part medially; spermathecal reservoirs sac-shaped, longer than wide, broadest proximally.
